stood guard here.

169
00:09:29,030 --> 00:09:30,250
When ordinary folk see them coming,

170
00:09:30,670 --> 00:09:31,580
they turn aside and make way

171
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,730
even from three li away.

172
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:36,130
