00:11:55,550 --> 00:11:56,940
Ever since the great battle atop the Imperial City

219
00:11:57,600 --> 00:12:00,530
between Baili Dongjun and Ye Dingzhi,

220
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:02,460
Tianqi City

221
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:04,610
